## Product constraints (please respect)

- **AR / passthrough first:** Design assumes **see-through** operation for safety; avoid opaque full-screen overlays during movement.  
- **Fork-friendly:** Avoid hard dependency on unreleased or undocumented Meta-only APIs without fallbacks.  
- **Small PRs:** Prefer incremental Meta integrations (passthrough layer ‚Üí mesh ‚Üí anchors) over monolithic rewrites.

